00:28:22,900 --> 00:28:24,799
It's time to get back to the council session though

689
00:28:24,799 --> 00:28:26,299
and figure out what is happening

690
00:28:26,299 --> 00:28:28,900
and where the adventures could be off to next.

691
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:29,799
Have a great week.

692
00:28:29,799 --> 00:28:30,600
We'll talk soon.

693
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,100
Lady Laral Silverhand,

694
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:39,000
she pipes up and she says,

695
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:44,000
I'm sorry you have ridded the misty forest of Kuth

696
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:48,000
and Nerenvane?

697
00:28:48,099 --> 00:28:52,299
Well, we drove them out of Kuth's lair.

698
00:28:52,299 --> 00:28:55,099
We're not sure where they are now.

699
00:28:55,099 --> 00:28:57,099
They were too strong for us to defeat

700
00:28:57,099 --> 00:29:00,099
even with the help of Delaine and Laskat.

701
00:29:00,099 --> 00:29:02,099
They were too powerful for us.

702
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:06,700
Yes, Delaine has been seen back in the city.

703
00:29:06,700 --> 00:29:10,299
He has not yet returned to the council.

704
00:29:10,299 --> 00:29:11,599
We weren't sure why,

705
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:13,599
but that could have something to do with it.

706
00:29:13,599 --> 00:29:17,599
Perhaps he himself is on the hunt.

707
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:18,400
I don't know.

708
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:19,800
I guess the more pressing matter,

709
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:21,800
the Dragon Council.

710
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:26,000
What of your meeting with the council

711
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:27,300
of the metallic dragons?

712
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:30,000
Do you want the short answer or the long answer?

713
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:34,000
Well, I guess will they help us?

714
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,600
They will,

715
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:39,200
but they've made demands

716
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:44,400
that will need to be met before they will help.

717
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:48,400
And if I may say, they're not unreasonable demands.

718
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,900
What are their demands?

719
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:53,700
And you see some of the other members

720
00:29:53,700 --> 00:29:57,400
kind of stirring in their seats a little bit.

721
00:29:57,400 --> 00:30:00,200
Reparations, for the most part.

722
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:05,400
People of our kind have been not kind to them.

723
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,300
Our history is terrible,

724
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:11,500
but the elven history specifically

725
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:14,300
and what we have done to the dragon kind

726
00:30:14,299 --> 00:30:16,399
is inexcusable.

727
00:30:16,399 --> 00:30:21,000
However, they are willing to help us

728
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:26,000
if a formal apology is given from you,

729
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,000
King Melandric.

730
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:29,899
From me, for what?

731
00:30:29,899 --> 00:30:31,000
For what she just said.

732
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:31,700
Listen to her.

733
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,799
Jesus Christ, right?

734
00:30:33,799 --> 00:30:36,200
The Drakorg mythal,

735
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:40,500
all dragons made agitated and turned to beasts.

736
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:42,299
That was the gold dragon pro-tanther

737
00:30:42,299 --> 00:30:44,599
that is looking for this apology.

738
00:30:44,599 --> 00:30:47,500
And if we give this apology,

739
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:51,000
they will help us.

740
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:54,200
The gold dragons will help us.

741
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:56,099
Just the gold.

742
00:30:56,099 --> 00:30:59,200
This is the demand from the gold dragons.

743
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:01,399
And I think an apology

744
00:31:01,399 --> 00:31:03,399
for the help that they can give us

745
00:31:03,399 --> 00:31:08,000
is a very, very small price to pay.

746
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:11,099
You're right.

747
00:31:11,100 --> 00:31:14,300
We pressed our luck long enough

748
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:15,500
against the cult of the dragon

749
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:19,600
and we need all the help we can get.

750
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:22,400
I will give them their apology.

751
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:25,500
I will make arrangements and do so.

752
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:27,000
Thank you.

753
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,500
You look around the room

754
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:31,700
and this is the fullest the room has ever been.

755
00:31:31,700 --> 00:31:35,400
There are a couple new faces in the room as well.

756
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:39,100
You look to the right of Lord Dagglet,

757
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:44,300
Never Ember and you see a female tiefling

758
00:31:44,300 --> 00:31:46,700
sitting quietly to his right

759
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:49,500
who you remember seeing

760
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:52,600
at the very first council session you were ever at.

761
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:54,000
And she was very much very similar

762
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,500
sitting quietly to herself.

763
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:59,900
You also see the ambassador from Mithril Hall,

764
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:02,000
Ambassador Conrad Braunenville,

765
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,500
sitting at the table

766
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:05,700
and he hasn't been to any council sessions

767
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:07,000
prior to this one.

768
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:11,799
Also in this room, you see another new face,

769
00:32:11,799 --> 00:32:16,599
an older man dressed in very luxurious robes.

770
00:32:16,599 --> 00:32:18,500
Delaine is not there,

771
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:21,200
but Remilia Haven Tree of the Harpers is there.

772
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:23,700
Anthaar Frum is there.

773
00:32:23,700 --> 00:32:27,099
And then the rest of the Lord's Alliance is also there.

774
00:32:27,099 --> 00:32:30,200
King Melandric, Sir Istival

775
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:34,000
and everybody else who you already know,

776
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,599
Lady Leral Silverhand and that's all.

777
00:32:36,600 --> 00:32:39,000
Is that dwarf that's there,

778
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:41,600
by incredible dwarven coincidence,

779
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:46,000
happen to be the one that Flint knows from Mithril Hall?

780
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,000
So that'd be amazing.

781
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,300
I do believe so.

782
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:50,500
I mean, yeah.

783
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:51,900
Yeah, that's the one.

784
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:53,100
He is the ambassador.

785
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:55,800
Good old Kenneth Branagh.

786
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:57,000
Kenneth Branagh?

787
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,600
I love that guy.

788
00:32:58,600 --> 00:32:59,600
He's good in everything.

789
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,200
He's very good.

790
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:04,400
Flint turns toward Conrad Braunenville

791
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:06,000
and he says,

792
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:09,100
the Silver Dragons agreed to help us

793
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:13,900
if we're able to get back something of theirs.

794
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:18,400
And he's not really kind of looking at you directly,

795
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:20,600
but turns when nobody else responds

796
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:26,000
and you mean us.

797
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:28,100
Yeah, Braunenville, I'm talking to you.

798
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:32,100
Keep up, over here.

799
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:33,600
Over here, bud, over here.

800
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:34,900
All right, all right.

801
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:37,300
Yep, yep, okay.

802
00:33:37,300 --> 00:33:38,100
What do we got?

803
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:38,800
We got gold.

804
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:40,900
We got...

805
00:33:40,900 --> 00:33:44,500
Oh, it's not quite anything like that.

